
=== VoodooPHP ==


1.3.1

Aug 30 2012
- Change versioning system
- Move Core\Upload to AddOn\UploadHandler\Handler
- Fix bugs in views files
- Added style.css && application.js in the module template
- Fixed HTACCESS to allow static files (.js,.css, etc) in Application and AddOn directory. Blocks anything else
- Added Core\Exception::sendToEmail
- Bootstrap 2.1
- jQuery 1.8
- Update magician's route

-------

1.3.0
Aug 3 2012
- Rename Autoloader

--------

1.2.0

- Fix bugs in Views::setPageTitle, Views::setPageDescription 

---------
- 5.3/1.1.0
July 19 2012
This version of Curl is backward incompatible
    * Voodoo\Core\HTTP\Curl
        - getResponse() return CurlResponse
        - call($METHOD) 
        - getHTTPCode()
        -> get($data), post($data)
    * Voodoo\Core\HTTP\CurlResponse
        - change jsonToArray to toArray()
        - removed httpCode(), to get the code use Core\Curl::getHTTPCode()
        - removed response()
        - added toString()
     * Voodoo\Paginator
        - Fix constant name
     * Voodoo\Forms
        - Simple form

---------
- 5.3/1.0.0
Friday July 13 2012
    - New versioning <PHPMajorVersion>.<PHPMinorVersion>/<VoodooMajor>.<VoodooMinor>.<VodooPatch>
    - PHP 5.3
    - Modular MVC
    - More setting in the module config
    - Dependency injection for views and pagination in the controller
